Pre-Game Insights: Germany's coach Julian Nagelsmann praised the midfield partnership of Aleksandar Pavlovic and Angelo Stiller for the upcoming match against Netherlands.
Pavlovic, returning from injury, will play a crucial role in the midfield alongside Stiller, who is making his third cap.
Others: Germany are aiming to secure a win after drawing 2-2 with Netherlands in their previous encounter.
The match is significant for Germany's preparation ahead of the 2026 World Cup.
